252
00:18:54,810 --> 00:18:58,470
I still remember the last time we went camping during college.

253
00:18:59,170 --> 00:19:01,810
Are you talking about our graduation trip?

254
00:19:01,810 --> 00:19:05,770
Fortunately, a certain someone wasn't cooking that time.

255
00:19:13,450 --> 00:19:17,150
Lawyer Zhen and Lawyer Fu, how did you meet Ying Ze?

256
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:20,270
You didn't meet each other at the laundromat, did you?

257
00:19:25,110 --> 00:19:27,320
We...

258
00:19:28,360 --> 00:19:31,960
