259
00:19:33,570 --> 00:19:35,730
His ex-wife brought the case to us;

260
00:19:35,730 --> 00:19:37,360
however, I thought it was a mutual consent divorce.

261
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:39,250
But he came to our office

262
00:19:39,250 --> 00:19:41,690
because there were custody issues.

263
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:47,170
