264
00:19:47,170 --> 00:19:51,960
That was the first time I'd encountered someone getting a divorce and thanking me.

265
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:57,140
Afterward, we frequently brought our clothes to the laundromat and became closer.

266
00:19:58,210 --> 00:20:02,110
I really wanted to thank you for helping me resolve that matter, Lawyer Zheng.

267
00:20:02,870 --> 00:20:07,330
At least, my ex-wife is the happiest than ever before.

268
00:20:07,330 --> 00:20:11,090
Our lives are respectively fine.

269
00:20:13,080 --> 00:20:15,150
And that's the best outcome.

270
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:20,440
You are really out of the ordinary.

271
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,400
We should probably get to bed.

272
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:39,060
What? It's still so early.

273
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:41,950
Everyone must be really tired.

274
00:20:44,870 --> 00:20:46,760
Let's go to bed.

275
00:20:47,950 --> 00:20:49,380
All right.

276
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:55,670
Well then, I won't bother the two of you.

277
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:06,340
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight.

278
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:19,450
Are you tired?

279
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:21,890
Do you want to go to bed?

280
00:21:22,770 --> 00:21:25,100
Did you grab your sleeping bag?

281
00:21:26,250 --> 00:21:28,350
I'm going to sleep in the car today.

282
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:30,490
That way, you can sleep with Ling Ling.

283
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:49,050
Or...

284
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:53,050
do you want to

285
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:55,370
sleep together in the tent today?

286
00:22:32,870 --> 00:22:34,460
Fu Ligong.

287
00:22:38,430 --> 00:22:40,550
- Come out of there.
- What's wrong?

288
00:22:40,550 --> 00:22:42,260
Come on out, quickly.

289
00:23:19,730 --> 00:23:23,110
Do you remember what happened senior year of high school?

290
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:25,110
Are you talking about...

291
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:29,530
when I was so drunk that I fell asleep in that classroom?

292
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:34,380
That was the first time I slept outside of my home.

293
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:37,060
I thought... it was pretty great.

294
00:23:38,830 --> 00:23:40,650
We were stuck outside in the middle of the night.

295
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:44,020
And there was an alcoholic by your side. You thought that was pretty great?

296
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:50,930
Although we couldn't see the stars at school,

297
00:23:50,930 --> 00:23:53,690
there were wild dogs barking in the middle of the night.

298
00:23:55,410 --> 00:23:59,480
But as long as you're by my side, I feel at ease.

299
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:30,320
Let's wake up tomorrow and watch the sunrise together.

300
00:24:32,260 --> 00:24:34,440
Are you certain you won't just dawdle in bed?

301
00:24:44,690 --> 00:24:46,200
I'll be like this.

